data.description: Stunning! Beautiful log home with many possibilities! This 4 bed, 2.75 bath home with 2700+ sqft is strategically located on nearly 2.5 acre and has something to offer everyone! From large households to generational living to short term rental options, etc. The open concept main floor boasts, dining room, living room, cozy pellet stove, kitchen,  primary bedroom with large 5 piece bath, walk in closet and territorial views. W/D hookups on both levels. Lower level also has complete kitchen, 3 bedrooms, bathroom and a bonus living room, all heated with a powerful radiant floor heating system. Don't miss the large 24x38 double bay garage and RV parking. Quick drive to Southworth Ferry, Hwy 16 or new Olalla store!
